* Research objective: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['What do you want to learn about your users or the problem you are addressing?'] }}

The previous AI Agent generated several user research questions:
{{ $('AI Agent: Question Editor').item.json.output }}

The designer reviewed these questions and gave feedback.  
Some were **approved**, some were **rejected**, and the reason why it is rejected.

Which question have been rejected: 
{{ $json.data['Which question have you not approved? Please write the number only.'] }}

Your task:
- Rewrite the questions that the user not approved. Use the users' feedback if it is available:
{{ $json.data['Why are they rejected?'] }}

Return your final output **only** in a list of questions (no markdown or extra text). Reset the numbering so it starts again from Question 01 in order.

